{"word":"Fort","slug":"fort","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Fort</b> A military defense.<br/> Field fortifications<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=20'>Deu 20:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=1'>2Ki 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4&verse=2'>Eze 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=17'>Eze 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=8'>Eze 26:8</a><br/> Defenses of cities<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=15'>2Ch 26:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=25&verse=12'>Isa 25:12</a><br/><a href='S:Castle'>Castle</a>; <a href='S:Tower'>Tower</a>; <a href='S:Walls'>Walls</a><br/> Erected in vineyards and herding grounds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=10'>2Ch 26:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=2'>Isa 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=33'>Mat 21:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=12&verse=1'>Mar 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=20&verse=9'>Luk 20:9</a><br/> Caves used for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=2'>Jdg 6:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=23&verse=29'>1Sa 23:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=33&verse=16'>Isa 33:16</a><br/> Figurative of God's care<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=3'>2Sa 22:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=47'>2Sa 22:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=18&verse=2'>Psa 18:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=31&verse=3'>Psa 31:3</a>; <a href='https: